{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01QRsYHJxTQkwh7AbDHMjM1t","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n## Changes Made\n\n### Problem\nScript step logs were buffered until step completion because `generic.Adapter` used `cmd.CombinedOutput()` which collects all output before returning.\n\n### Fix (4 files)\n\n1. **`internal/adapters/agents/generic/generic.go`** — Added `StatusWriter` field and `executeStreaming()` method. When StatusWriter is set, pipes stdout/stderr and streams each line through `StatusWriter.Log()` in real-time instead of buffering with `CombinedOutput()`.\n\n2. **`internal/agent/runner.go`** — Wires the `StatusWriter` into the generic adapter so script steps stream output through the same status protocol path that agent/prompt steps use.\n\n3. **`internal/protocol/status.go`** — Added flush support: after each JSON status message is encoded, calls `Flush()` on the underlying writer if it implements the `flusher` interface, ensuring immediate delivery.\n\n4. **`internal/logstream/logstream.go`** — Added `file.Sync()` after each log write to ensure the unified `full.log` is flushed to disk immediately.\n\n### Tests Added\n- `TestGenericAdapter_StreamsOutputViaStatusWriter` — verifies each output line is streamed as a separate `MsgLog`\n- `TestGenericAdapter_StreamsStderrViaStatusWriter` — verifies stderr is also streamed\n- `TestGenericAdapter_StreamingWithMarker` — verifies result markers work with streaming\n- `TestGenericAdapter_StreamingOnFailure` — verifies streaming works on failed commands\n- `TestRunner_ScriptStepStreamsLogs` — end-to-end test verifying log messages appear between `step_started` and `step_completed` in the status stream\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":286,"cache_read_input_tokens":71930,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":286},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b192fff1-2075-40cb-b513-cbbf26873af4","uuid":"5b0609fa-796d-4b9a-b050-317edc895e3e"}
